ection of your various personal data such as your name, surname, e-mail address will be the use of a right, the legitimate interests of our Company and, in limited circumstances, your explicit consent. It is mandatory for the data controller to fulfill its legal responsibility and it is mandatory for the legitimate interests of the data controller, provided that it is obligatory for the data controller to fulfill his legal responsibility. </p> <p> 4. Your Rights Regarding Your Personal Data </ p> <p> In accordance with the Communiqué on the Procedures and Principles of Application to the Data Officer, Justice Mah. Şehit Polis Fethi Sekin Cad. No 4 / B Bayraklı / İzmir in writing or from your e-mail address registered in our system to the e-mail address info@invismile.com.tr. </p> </div></div>"
